Format:
	Header:
		15 3A 4E 44 64 00 01 00 01
	String Length x2 - 2bytes:
		has to suit 4n+2 where n>0
	Middle:
		05 7F hex{{128 - (bytelength times 2)}} 3A
	String data:
		Starting in 00 01
		Ascii data
		Pad to length with 00
	Ending byte:
		CheckSum 8 bit 2s comp, +80hex,128dec if paddingbytes <= 2
